These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: garlic, kiwi, mango
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur, paramedic
1. the person eating garlic is in an even position##4
2. the accountant is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
3. the accountant is the person eating kiwi##1
4. the person eating mango is on the far left##1
5. the entrepreneur is the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | mango | garlic | kiwi |
| Job    | entrepreneur    | paramedic | accountant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, dancing, photography
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, helicopter, ship
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | dancing | photography | singing |
| Transport   | ship    | helicopter     | car        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, hiking, rock-climbing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, techno, gospel
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of indie##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing     | hiking | singing |
| Music-Genre   | techno | indie     | gospel  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, documentary, scientific
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, soccer, baseball
1. the person watching documentary movies is the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | documentary  | comedy  |
| Sport         | rowing  | soccer | baseball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, sudoku, fishing
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, mexican, spanish
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the chinese##2
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
3. the spanish is on the left of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | cooking   | fishing | sudoku    |
| Nationality   | mexican | spanish     | chinese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, dancing, photography
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, skateboarding, water-polo
1. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | dancing | photography | singing   |
| Sport   | water-polo     | surfing    | skateboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, zombie, disaster
3 different pets are kept: fish, cat, mouse
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching western movies is between the owner of the mouse and the person watching disaster movies##2
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the owner of the fish is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | western | zombie |
| Pet           | cat         | fish         | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, lemon, garlic
3 different pets are kept: ferret, dog, horse
1. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the dog and the person eating kiwi##2
2. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | lemon | garlic | kiwi |
| Pet    | dog    | ferret | horse     |

