.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, disco, trance
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, skiing, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the fan of metal##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the fan of disco##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | disco  | metal  |
| Sport         | rowing | skiing | rugby |

