.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water, tea
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, orange, banana
1. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person eating banana is in an even position##4
3. the person eating banana is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | tea      | water |
| Food       | orange | banana | eggplant   |

