.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, card-games, puzzles
3 different pets are kept: fish, chinchilla, guinea-pig
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the owner of the chinchilla##2
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | card-games | puzzles | woodworking |
| Pet     | fish    | guinea-pig  | chinchilla   |

