.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, dog, goat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, snowboarding, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Pet     | dog  | goat   | ferret |
| Sport   | water-polo | snowboarding | rugby       |

 